1. Kada sam vozio bicikl, ispao mi je lanac. (*ispao*) (When I was riding my bike, the chain fell off.)
2. Ako ne budeš pažljiv, ispašćeš na ispitu. (*ispašćeš*) (If you're not careful, you'll fail the exam.)
3. Ako se dobro organizujemo, ovaj projekat neće ispasti loše. (*ispasti*) (If we organize well, this project won't turn out bad.)
4. Ona je bila ljuta kada je saznala da je njen plan ispao u vodu. (*ispao*) (She was angry when she found out her plan fell through.)
5. Svi su bili iznenađeni kada je on ispao heroj. (*ispao*) (Everyone was surprised when he turned out to be a hero.)
6. Čekao sam ga ispred restorana, ali on nikada nije ispo. (*ispo*) (I waited for him outside the restaurant, but he never showed up.)
7. Iako su mnogi sumnjali u nju, ona je na kraju ispala pobjednik. (*ispala*) (Although many doubted her, she ended up being the winner.)
8. Moram da pazim da mi ne ispadnu naočare iz džepa. (*ispadnu*) (I have to be careful not to drop my glasses from my pocket.)